{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"HTMLContentElement","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLContentElement","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLContentElement\"><code>HTMLContentElement</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Propriedades</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLContentElement/getDistributedNodes\"><code>getDistributedNodes()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLContentElement/select\"><code>select</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Páginas relacionadas a Web Components</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/CustomElementRegistry\"><code>CustomElementRegistry</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Document/createElement\"><code>Document.createElement()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/attachShadow\"><code>Element.attachShadow()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/shadowRoot\"><code>Element.shadowRoot</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/slot\"><code>Element.slot</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Event/composed\"><code>Event.composed</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Event/composedPath\"><code>Event.composedPath</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLSlotElement\"><code>HTMLSlotElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTemplateElement\"><code>HTMLTemplateElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/getRootNode\"><code>Node.getRootNode()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Node/isConnected\"><code>Node.isConnected</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ShadowRoot\"><code>ShadowRoot</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/customElements\"><code>Window.customElements</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p></p><div class=\"notecard deprecated\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Deprecated:</strong> This feature is no longer recommended. Though some browsers might still support it, it may have already been removed from the relevant web standards, may be in the process of being dropped, or may only be kept for compatibility purposes. Avoid using it, and update existing code if possible; see the <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">compatibility table</a> at the bottom of this page to guide your decision. Be aware that this feature may cease to work at any time.</p></div><p></p>\n\n<p>A interface do&nbsp;<code><strong>HTMLContentElement</strong></code> representa&nbsp;um&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/content\"><code>&lt;content&gt;</code></a> Element HTML, ao qual é usado em&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Web_Components/Using_shadow_DOM\">Shadow DOM</a>.&nbsp;</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties","title":"Propriedades","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>Esta interface herda&nbsp;as&nbsp;propriedades&nbsp;de&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a>.</em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"htmlcontentelement.select\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLContentElement/select\"><code>HTMLContentElement.select</code></a></dt>\n <dd>é um&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a> que reflete&nbsp;o&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/content#attr-select\"><code>select</code></a> attributo&nbsp;HTML . O&nbsp;valor&nbsp;é&nbsp;uma&nbsp;lista de vírgula separada&nbsp;dos seletores&nbsp;CSS que&nbsp;selecionam o&nbsp;conteúdo para inserir&nbsp;em&nbsp;lugar&nbsp;do&nbsp;elemento&nbsp;<code>&lt;content&gt;</code>.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"méthodos","title":"Méthodos","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>Esta interface herda&nbsp;os&nbsp;méthodos de&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a>.</em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"htmlcontentelement.getdistributednodes\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLContentElement/getDistributedNodes\"><code>HTMLContentElement.getDistributedNodes()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Retorna&nbsp;um&nbsp;static <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/NodeList\"><code>NodeList</code></a> do <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"A documentação sobre isto ainda não foi escrita; por favor considere contribuir!\">distributed nodes</a> associado&nbsp;com&nbsp;este&nbsp;elemento&nbsp;<code>&lt;content&gt;</code>.&nbsp;</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specificações","title":"Specificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"spec-table standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specificações</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Commentários</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/webcomponents/spec/shadow/#the-content-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Shadow DOM<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'content' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-obsolete\">Obsoleto</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect3\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Componentes</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari (WebKit)</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte&nbsp;Básico</td>\n   <td>35</td>\n   <td><span style=\"font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/28\" title=\"Released on 2014-03-18.\">28</a> (28)</span>&nbsp;[1]</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td>26</td>\n   <td><span style=\"font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Phone</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td>37</td>\n   <td>28.0 (28) [1]</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<p>[1] Se Shadow DOM não é&nbsp;habilitado&nbsp;no&nbsp;Firefox, &lt;content&gt; elementos vai se comportar como <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLUnknownElement\"><code>HTMLUnknownElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>. Shadow DOM foi a primeira implementação do&nbsp;Firefox 28 e está&nbsp;atrásde uma preferência , <code>dom.webcomponents.enabled</code>, qual é desabilitado por padrão.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>O elemento&nbsp;HTML&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/content\"><code>&lt;content&gt;</code></a> , implementa&nbsp;esta&nbsp;interface.</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Web_Components/Using_shadow_DOM\">Shadow DOM</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"sect4\">&nbsp;</dt>\n</dl>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Propriedades","id":"properties"},{"text":"Méthodos","id":"méthodos"},{"text":"Specificações","id":"specificações"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"A interface do HTMLContentElement representa um <content> Element HTML, ao qual é usado em Shadow DOM.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"HTMLContentElement","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"HTMLContentElement","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"HTMLContentElement","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"HTMLContentElement","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"HTMLContentElement","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/htmlcontentelement","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/htmlcontentelement/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API","title":"APIs da Web"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLContentElement","title":"HTMLContentElement"}],"pageTitle":"HTMLContentElement - APIs da Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}